mparison\nprovides an empirical answer to the above question and demonstrates the\npracticality of atomic MWMR register implementations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2011 09:50:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Apr 2012 13:51:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-04-10"}
